Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*不要东躲西藏*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*献出我的心*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*它就能有节奏地*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*永跳不止*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*生命如此短暂*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠  你唱的什么歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我梦里的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很好听哦  -*为什么...*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特蕾西发了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新沙发来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想象中更绿一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是照片的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠  你还好吗  菠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还在跟着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下  抓牢车子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了 抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带菠走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话给钱宁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他他们找到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我来了  -她失去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤到哪里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要急救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这能让你舒服一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别伤害她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她放下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她放下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别移动她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打急救电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以告诉救护员  你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(172,210)\bord0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK}金斯兰监狱  佐治亚州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒  塔特  伙计  你的神父来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们总这么玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在里面没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没要求见神父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有相当长的暴力史  塔特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被捕是十四岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后还因为抢劫和伤人多次入狱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  你因两起谋杀罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在半小时内被处决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你没什么要忏悔的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无辜的  我是被陷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过貌似没人相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没人相信过你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天行刑  却没有家人朋友来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你服刑这七年  也从未有人来过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持活下去的希望都是很难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括想要记住曾经的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要忏悔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生存的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都在寻求宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无人寻得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来帮你逃狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是割伤和挫伤对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  但她还没恢复意识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要确保没有内伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她的大脑图吗  出错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-大脑系统确实在运作  -再测一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下  马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是答应了  你有什么要求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来不仅是为了还你自由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要给你份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚一男一女死于车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是一个叫菠的小女孩的养父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温特  小心信号声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不是场意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想要绑架这个小女孩却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在在圣安妮医院  我们得在别人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是个绑匪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有要你绑架她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来请你救她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小女孩非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你还有4分54秒的时间逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这很好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有考虑吗  还是只是固执己见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可在给你一条出路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离牧师远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4分28秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凭什么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信那些所谓的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-够了  -你以为我为什么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了吗  -好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一支肾上腺素  一支阿托品[含颠茄]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了吗  -好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生  可以结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡时间  晚上11点58分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽行过死荫的幽谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\an8}出自旧约圣经《诗篇》第二十三章\N通常是为死刑犯最后的祷词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怕遭害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有五十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  他们说只是打砸抢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们陷害了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关灯  关闭系统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手呢  把你手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有脚镣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  现在打他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来  打我  -贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往左边走  左边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  我们得快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦斯奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  他往那边跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他往那边跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿平静与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也"很高兴"见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  住手  关了它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  我叫温特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要飞几个小时  飞机上聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这计划如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没让你们铐着他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有点过于"积极"了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开他的手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么选他  他是个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不选我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我们晚点再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫菠对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是库里安医生  是这里的住院医师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这乌龟很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫斯坦利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妈妈送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的亲生妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我不记得她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还需要做几项检查  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场车祸很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此我很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们才做了我两个星期的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们那么和蔼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个房间的病人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好医生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了丝尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是丝尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  你还照顾过他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了  菠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚点再来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senga怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我不认识叫丝尼格的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是斯古洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯古洛斯  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小女孩现在圣安妮医院里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我明天就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温特会保护她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-弥尔顿·温特吗  -是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就想让大家这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说得很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚不工作  今天是我妈妈生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是在圣安妮医院的八楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到她后联系我  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,220)\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs18\b1}我很荣幸将今年的人道主义奖颁给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,240)\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs18\b1}罗曼·斯古洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打菠出生  就一直有神秘现象发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些现象无法预测
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是和她的情绪有关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她还控制不了那力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会长大成才的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个被冤入狱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能掰弯勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生  这是很非常真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冤入狱的那位也是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还可以掰弯小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想在适当的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她为世界所用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有权势的人会试图绑架她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想把她全部天赋都据为己用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们觉得控制了她的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就控制了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么选我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新科技  全球定位追踪装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能确切地知道你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是为了保证你做完任务会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想脱下它  只能砍掉自己的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我会咬掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟后降落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会给我配枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生  你和好人共事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不上枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗  你辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是因为这件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为你感到遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}祝爷爷早日康复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该在重症监护病房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过急诊室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她回来  然后跟桑托斯会合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他躺下吧  开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动  现在正好有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从梯子上跌落  受力两臂有挫伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还算稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还算好  还有情况更糟的  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  -不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下  里面那个女孩去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况稳定了  转移到了普通病房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摔进了下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们给我洗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撞到头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸上的伤是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  你根本不觉得疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能摸一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的新养父吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  你太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跟你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就得跟我走  温特说了你必须跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥尔顿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是温特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫弥尔顿·温特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你为什么哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说过了  伤很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是因为你想起来了你是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她去拍个片子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  我跟你们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  我会带你过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我带她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会害我丢了工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾兰医生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色有些发白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想良心不安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子别这么调皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那边走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下  别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦停车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会平安无事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谁  -追我们的那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在她屁股上狠狠扎了一针
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会没事的  我才不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们这是去哪  -我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-弥尔顿在哪  -我说了不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能安静一会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}城市理发店
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道丝尼格是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是普通病人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得告诉特里医生  这样他就不会辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女儿下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我自己也有安排  -很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽力了  可他没吃多少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以周日再付我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  卡门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个今天病人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救他  但没成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  以前也看过人死  但
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人  我真的很想救他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得你以前总跟我说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说就算我是地球上最后一个医生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不会来找我看病
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是那么强壮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么多想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你生病后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总想着要治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是  总是想让你恢复健康
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你知道你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.27,0:23:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你会感谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道我今天辞职了  你会很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是要争到最后做赢的那一个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你却没法再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.84,0:24:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找地址
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能像那样直接跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.15,0:24:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去奥斯维奥街14-22号
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.54,0:24:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡言乱语些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得告诉特里医生关于丝尼格的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.24,0:24:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个小屁孩能闭嘴听我讲话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.59,0:24:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那21任养父母也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.99,0:24:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你很傻  英语说得也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩  快进来  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-钱宁  -我们得赶快走  快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:24:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.46,0:25:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.32,0:25:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该回救护车上的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.46,0:25:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.41,0:25:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个家伙把我打了个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.43,0:25:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是家伙  是个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.95,0:25:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我就是说  -一个女的把你打了个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.81,0:25:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.47,0:25:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个女的  长得很高大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一点都不高大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.81,0:25:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.18,0:25:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.54,0:25:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来让我抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.93,0:25:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又重了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.89,0:25:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有  我两周之前才和你见过
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.46,0:25:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱宁  带菠去看看新衣服  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.27,0:25:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些很漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.39,0:25:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-塔特先生  -我的脚环
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.14,0:25:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把它拿掉  -没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.26,0:25:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有过协定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.51,0:25:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是你为我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作我已经做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.98,0:26:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.52,0:26:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你已经注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.39,0:26:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠是个非常特殊的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.11,0:26:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作是保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保她的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.93,0:26:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让那个女人伤害她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.31,0:26:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人  以及她所效力的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.07,0:26:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会成为我的新养父吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.15,0:26:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.77,0:26:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很凶  而且身上很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.78,0:26:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掉到下水道里了  我都告诉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.45,0:26:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  她也不想和我待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.05,0:26:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.37,0:26:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最重要的责任  例如她的健康
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.70,0:26:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及她的教育  那是你的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.60,0:26:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温特  我想和你待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.68,0:26:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来宝贝  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.73,0:26:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.58,0:26:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经谈过了  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.24,0:26:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我接受的话  这工作需要几个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.49,0:26:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.69,0:26:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要几个月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会是你一生中最精彩的几年
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.40,0:27:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用了五年时间才找到线索
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.92,0:27:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你只用了一天就跟丢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.49,0:27:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你够了  蠢货  发现什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.34,0:27:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔的摩地区仅有的相关资料是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.16,0:27:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温特在死前一年购买的房产
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.03,0:27:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址是新柯克街
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16-105号  看上去像个仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.74,0:27:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在把坐标发到你的GPS上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.26,0:27:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  转一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.36,0:27:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.43,0:27:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.63,0:27:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方的本事大得很
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.51,0:27:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量避免使用电话和其他电子设备
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.45,0:27:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱宁会监控你的行踪和进展
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.13,0:27:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我还没同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.12,0:27:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.82,0:27:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满世界都在通缉你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.41,0:27:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联调局  警察  所有人都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.71,0:27:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我可以碰碰运气
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.16,0:27:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出去之后十分钟都坚持不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.53,0:27:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一看到你就会射杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.31,0:28:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有了我们的帮助  你就不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.84,0:28:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是超级英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.01,0:28:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们是勤奋努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.95,0:28:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.60,0:28:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.66,0:28:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么选我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.77,0:28:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你好好照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.32,0:28:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育她  给她吃有机食品
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.93,0:28:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她住舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.59,0:28:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从现在开始要抚养她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.13,0:28:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一把枪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.38,0:28:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.14,0:28:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.78,0:28:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次看到她时就有所感觉  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.42,0:28:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.35,0:28:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.10,0:28:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.75,0:29:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.60,0:29:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.33,0:29:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上菠
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.00,0:29:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么找到我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.89,0:29:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问要去哪一层
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.87,0:29:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.95,0:29:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-斯坦利  -别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别捡了  快走  -不  斯坦利
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.30,0:29:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快点  -快走
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.81,0:29:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.74,0:29:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.79,0:29:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.40,0:30:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.68,0:30:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦利
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.18,0:31:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科里  他们之前在这里  现在走了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.97,0:31:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还能去什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.19,0:31:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查查别的房子  别的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.77,0:31:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再查查
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.67,0:31:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.04,0:31:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  拇指姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.09,0:31:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开她
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温特
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.65,0:31:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你不打女人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.88,0:31:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在打了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.73,0:31:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.19,0:31:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.37,0:31:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.98,0:32:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.19,0:32:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.72,0:32:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.59,0:33:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.01,0:33:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.23,0:33:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-钱怎么办  -别管钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.59,0:33:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.18,0:33:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.57,0:33:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.62,0:33:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了  没事了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.66,0:33:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是闹鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.69,0:33:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点吓人  不过没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.43,0:33:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-温特  -再快点  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.02,0:34:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.15,0:34:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所有的据点都不安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.93,0:34:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们得不断转移
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.89,0:34:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会拖住她
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.82,0:34:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在就得下车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.94,0:34:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.45,0:34:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.38,0:34:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.90,0:34:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别相信任何人  我们会去找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.47,0:34:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.15,0:34:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  带上钱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.24,0:34:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上钱  躲那儿去  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.86,0:34:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14-20
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.10,0:34:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120美元要过三年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.85,0:34:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.93,0:34:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.35,0:34:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.91,0:34:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那事儿  你怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.01,0:34:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.22,0:34:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刚才那群鸟  很诡异  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.96,0:34:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那经常发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.07,0:34:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想提那事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.02,0:35:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.81,0:35:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说饼干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.96,0:35:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-特里  -不行  咱们走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.91,0:35:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠  你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.75,0:35:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要跟你说丝尼格的事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.45,0:35:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.45,0:35:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.55,0:35:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个坏女人开枪打了他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.63,0:35:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你受了枪伤  -不算什么  我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.17,0:35:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个医生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.77,0:35:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个非常出色的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.37,0:35:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你中了枪  我们必须报警
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.49,0:35:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先帮我止一下血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.42,0:35:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.11,0:35:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  进屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.73,0:35:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这没有麻醉剂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.98,0:35:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缝上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.52,0:35:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  坐到桌子上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.85,0:35:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀起你的衬衫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.27,0:35:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.54,0:35:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.66,0:36:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不省人事了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.33,0:36:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时日不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.43,0:36:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很为你自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.29,0:36:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他不会
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.17,0:36:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.15,0:36:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝尼格怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.64,0:36:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你我不知道那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.48,0:36:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道  -抗生素
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.88,0:36:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你认识丝尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.00,0:36:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时会弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.21,0:36:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再深呼吸一次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.36,0:36:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还不认识她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.69,0:36:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你会认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.54,0:36:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可能会有点疼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.65,0:36:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽量不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.69,0:36:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天她会病得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.16,0:36:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你能救她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.16,0:36:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你她才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.85,0:36:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.40,0:36:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝尼格是个歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.94,0:36:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  她非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.24,0:37:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们难过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.68,0:37:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的音乐能让他们开心起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.75,0:37:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会治好她
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.33,0:37:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.26,0:37:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会治好很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.67,0:37:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你救治他这样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再缝一针就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.02,0:37:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲认为你是个好医生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.72,0:37:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道你努力想治好他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.32,0:37:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道他之前错了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很抱歉从没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.29,0:37:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.78,0:37:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.83,0:38:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.63,0:38:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别沾水  尽量别搬东西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.76,0:38:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要报警吗  -算了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.96,0:38:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么知道这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.17,0:38:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.86,0:38:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是这么讨人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.55,0:38:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.61,0:38:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先进行胸外按压  准备好手术室
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.41,0:38:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分钟内赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.54,0:38:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.78,0:38:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.49,0:38:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上运动衫  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.18,0:38:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡门  我是亚当
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.79,0:38:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道事出突然  但你得过来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.98,0:38:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被叫去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.87,0:38:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.38,0:39:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再见了  菠  -再见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.73,0:39:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.46,0:39:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我们到底去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.45,0:39:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费城
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.17,0:39:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脾气不好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.00,0:39:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你想跟我走  去另一个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.58,0:39:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得定几条规矩  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.91,0:39:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.01,0:39:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.66,0:39:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个医生不关你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.55,0:39:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.38,0:39:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是他把你治好的  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.21,0:39:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.47,0:39:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到了别的地方  你少管别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.91,0:39:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.45,0:39:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有姑娘掉进河里怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.58,0:39:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎  快向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.41,0:39:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我看到有人在路上逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.29,0:39:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那天特别热
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.46,0:39:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热到掉个硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能直接融化在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.50,0:39:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去捡硬币手被黏住
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.73,0:39:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一辆卡车正迎面而来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.68,0:39:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这根本不可能  -如果真的发生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.03,0:40:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}来电  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.40,0:40:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她叫什么名字  -艾格尼丝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.51,0:40:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾格尼丝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.66,0:40:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温特  手背怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.44,0:40:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又被保护起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.02,0:40:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.79,0:40:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被塔特保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.19,0:40:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得说这有点出人意料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.57,0:40:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这事早晚会出岔子的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.03,0:40:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯古洛斯越逼越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.88,0:40:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不敢相信咱们以前居然和那种人一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.70,0:40:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过往总是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.51,0:40:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很神奇的  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.46,0:40:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得不断地让他们在各城市间转移
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.02,0:40:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那太冒险了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.45,0:41:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们向好处看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.45,0:41:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想那些她一路上能够帮助到的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.88,0:41:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你找了个死刑犯当她同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.12,0:41:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.92,0:41:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.87,0:41:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有月亮的碎片砸到了一间房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.31,0:41:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里他们把蜘蛛关在笼子里  笼子坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.81,0:41:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后尼桑姆那里有个种田人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.07,0:41:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对蜘蛛过敏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.59,0:41:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这句话槽点太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.39,0:41:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二规矩是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一切照我说的做  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.07,0:41:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果我们正呆在冰屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.96,0:41:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你患上了寒冷肿瘤什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.05,0:41:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你叫我点蜡烛  可我闻到了瓦斯味
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.74,0:41:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  一定要点蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.83,0:41:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艾格尼丝
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.85,0:42:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}丝尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.40,0:42:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会好起来的
